Company Overview of Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Lord Abbett & Co. LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in dividend paying value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations, with a focus on large-cap and mid-cap companies within the market capitalization range of the S&P 900 Index. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach with a focus on factors such as companies with a ten-year history of ...
Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Lord Abbett & Co. LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in dividend paying value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations, with a focus on large-cap and mid-cap companies within the market capitalization range of the S&P 900 Index. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach with a focus on factors such as companies with a ten-year history of dividend issuance and growth, financial condition, near-term earnings, long-term normalized earnings, earnings growth rates, changes in economic and financial environment; new or improved products or services; changes in management or structure of the company; price increases for the company’s products or services; and improved efficiencies resulting from new technologies or changes in distribution, valuation and risk models and other quantitative analytical tools, and assessment of these portfolio characteristics to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index and S&P 900 10-Year Dividend Growth Index. It conducts proprietary research to create its portfolio. The fund was formerly known as Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Capital Structure Fund. Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund was formed on December 27, 2001 and is domiciled in the United States.
