Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund Key Developments

Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Nov 05, 2015
Aug 20 15
Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Nov 05, 2015., at 09:00 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: offices of Lord, Abbett & Co. LLC. Agenda: To approve a proposal to amend the fundamental investment restriction of each fund regarding borrowing; to approve a proposal to amend the fundamental investment restriction of each Fund regarding lending; and to ratify the selection of Deloitte & Touche LLP as the independent registered public accounting firm for each Fund’s current fiscal year.


