Company Overview of Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of November 22, 2013, Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund has been acquired by Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund. Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Lord, Abbett & Co. LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap companies. It typically employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of i...
As of November 22, 2013, Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund has been acquired by Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Calibrated Dividend Growth Fund. Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Lord, Abbett & Co. LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap companies. It typically employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 1000 Index and the S&P 500 Index. It was formerly known as Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Large Cap Core Fund. Lord Abbett Research Fund, Inc. - Lord Abbett Classic Stock Fund was formed on June 3, 1992 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


90 Hudson StreetJersey City, NJ 07302-3973United StatesFounded in 1992



